---
alwaysApply: true
---
# ==== ANDROID PROJECT SAFETY RULES ====

- rule: "AI dilarang mengubah file Gradle"
  triggers:
    - "build.gradle"
    - "build.gradle.kts"
    - "settings.gradle"
    - "settings.gradle.kts"
    - "gradle.properties"
    - "gradle-wrapper.properties"
    - "gradle/wrapper/*"
  action:
    - "Jangan modifikasi file ini"
    - "Jika user meminta perubahan gradle, minta konfirmasi dulu"
    - "Jika perubahan diperlukan agar fitur berjalan, berikan instruksi saja, jangan ubah file-nya"

- rule: "Jangan menginstall dependency baru tanpa konfirmasi"
  action:
    - "Jika diperlukan library baru, beri rekomendasi dulu, tunggu user setuju"
